In the age of AI, discerning what’s real from what’s fake has never been more urgent. With mass-produced content and convincing deepfakes everywhere, how can Catholics find the truth online?

In this episode of Catholic Futurist, host @BenjaminCrockett joins @JoséManuelDeUrquidi (@JuanDiegoNetwork) and @MatthewHarveySanders (@Longbeard) to explore tools for discernment, the responsibilities of tech platforms, and the need for strong Catholic formation.

Video Timestamps
01:30 – AI’s Promise & Peril
03:33 – The Deepfake Problem
05:50 – How to Fight Deception
12:54 – Rise of "Digital Missionaries"
18:37 – Online Faith, Offline Community